{
  "stem": "14387.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just got to Vladivostok and hoping they would get someplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We fortunately had all our reservations made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we stayed in Vladivostok a few days, and then we got on a Japanese ship to cross to Japan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, the Norwegian government had told us that we would have to travel third class all the way because there was a limited amount of money here, but we would have to take first class on Vladivostok to Japan.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said that's a terrible ship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had first-class tickets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a baby buggy with me which I carried with the baby to have it for the baby all the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a ridiculous thing to take but you see things were different in those days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big buggy, a four-wheeled thing that didn't fold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had this with me all along because I'd insisted how am I going to carry this baby around?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later on it got stolen in Los Angeles, but it's kind of incidental.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a rather strange thing to take a buggy all around the world and have it stolen in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a big, white leatherette thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we got on-- we were going to get on the boat in Vladivostok and, well, the boat was kind of docked just a little way away from the dock.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to get onto it you had to go over a rope bridge with a couple-- we had three suitcases, mostly full of diapers because we didn't take any of our valuables with us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was all left in Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, as long as I'm telling you, I'll tell you what happened to the valuables-- the silver mostly, but I'll go back and tell you.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
